    <h3 class="apn-c-h3" style="margin-top:40px;">The 4-Week Competitor Protocol</h3>
    <p class="apn-c-body">Each week has one focus, one set of actions, and one measurable output. Follow the sequence. Do not skip ahead.</p>

    <!-- Week 1 -->
    <div class="apn-c-week-block">
      <span class="apn-c-week-label">Week 1: Identification and Lock-In</span>
      <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:#0D0D0D;">Focus: Confirm your primary gap. Start one protocol. Pause everything else.</p>
      <ul class="apn-c-checklist">
        <li>Review your Gap 1 from Module 3. Accept that this is the single lever for the next four weeks.</li>
        <li>Start one protocol specific to Gap 1. If sleep: set a fixed wake time and keep it seven days straight. If nutrition: hit 25g to 30g protein within 45 minutes of training, every session. If recovery: implement one active recovery session between your two hardest training days.</li>
        <li>Write the protocol down. Put it somewhere visible. Habit consolidation increases by 30% when a target behavior is written and visible daily.</li>
        <li>Pause all other protocol changes. Nothing new is added this week except the one Gap 1 action.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
