      Moving from Competitor to Elite is a shift from closing primary gaps to optimizing closed systems. Elite athletes don't discover new pillars to build. They refine existing ones with greater precision: bloodwork markers, sleep stage architecture, micronutrient accuracy, and HRV-informed training load management. To reach Elite, your primary gap must be functionally closed, not just improved. That is the standard this four-week protocol is designed to help you meet.
    </p>

  </div>
</div>


